# Welcome to the main.tas entrypoint! Examples of 2 commands are included below, but the real example is in the file linked in @read_file
# Feel free to edit this file directly while you're testing, or to start building segments to chain them together for longer TAS efforts

# Set a frame rate,, or uncap it with -1
@frame_rate=-1

# Read a file (allows for composing segments) from `./inputs`
@read_file=to-first-clone
